skdetail:
Rated: Mature. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: never have i ever
des: This skill is perfect when you are playing the popular party game: Never Have I Ever! Also known as I Never, you'll be having a blast playing with your friends, when all of a sudden you can't think of a new question for the game... No problem! Just ask Alexa and she will read out a random Never Have I Ever question from a database of over 1500 statements!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
